    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, with documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis has been professionally reinforced to address subframe integrity, complemented by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a fresh M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every bushing, seal, and suspension component is in peak operating condition, ensuring the precise handling characteristics and linear torque delivery this platform is celebrated for. No deferred maintenance; purely an enthusiast-grade specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
